Let’s make a game!
  name:Omega Clicker
  by:Gubby
  version:1.0
 
Settings
  building cost increase:125%
 
Buttons
 
  *omega
    name:Omega
    desc:Click this to get Omegas.
    on click:yield 1 omegas
 
Resources
  *omegas|om
    name:Omega[s?omegas]
    desc:The final letter in Greek.
  *highscore|hs
    name:Highest Omegas
    desc:Your highscore
    is always:om:max
 
Upgrades
  *up1|ob
    name:Omega Batteries
    desc:Boosts Omegas!
 
  *up2|sb
    name:Speed Boost
    desc:Boosts your Psis.
 
Buildings
  *psi|ps
    name:Psi
    desc:A psi that makes omegas twice a second.
    cost:50 omegas
    on tick:give 2 om
 
Shinies
*luckyGnome
  name:Lucky gnome
  on click:yield (random(7,77)) om
  movement:anywhere fade bounce moveRandom
  frequency:120
